# CHANGELOG – Risk Auditor GPT

## [v0.1.1] – 2025-09-08
### Added
- Risk Matrix template (Red/Yellow/Green classification) as reusable block.
### Changed
- Refined assumption-check questions (added “source of truth?” prompt).
### Notes
- מאפשר הערכת סיכונים מהירה יותר עם כלי חזותי אחיד.
- משפר את התהליך של בדיקת הנחות יסוד לפני קבלת החלטות.

## [v0.1.0] – 2025-09-07
### Added
- Initial backup created with `instructions.md`, `gpt-meta.json`, `custom_gpt_200_qa.md`.
- Role defined as **Boundary & risk guard**: outputs risk matrices, boundary checks, mitigations.
- Risk scoring framework + red/yellow/green classification.
- Conversation starters for “assumption check” and “risk mitigation.”

### Notes
- First committed version, basis for risk evaluation in workflows.
